@484   = ~Albert~
@485   = ~We met the "Lizard King" of Dragon's Eye. He informed us that the upper caves of the volcano belonged to him.  He also indicated that he was brought to the caves by someone named Yxunomei.  Apparently, the lizard men do the bidding of Yxunomei to feed his people.  They abduct the villagers for food and for Yxunomei.~
@486   = ~You are free to ask, traveler.  I promise no answers. ~ [EVER_01]
@487   = ~Tempus is the god of war, is he not?~
@488   = ~I come to show respect to your god and his worshippers, Everard.  Still, there is not much battle to be had here in Easthaven, I hope?~
@489   = ~Tempus is the god of war.  Easthaven seems far removed from any battles.~
@490   = ~Accalia told me to ask you about "Jerrod's Stone."  She said it has something to do with one of your holy days.~
@491   = ~I wished to hear the tale of Jerrod's Stone again. ~
@492   = ~You carry the scars of war, Everard.  Were you wounded in battle?~
@493   = ~Do you know anything about the expedition that Hrothgar's putting together?~
@494   = ~I heard there was a messenger who came to the temple from Kuldahar. ~
@495   = ~I was wondering if we might pay our respects to the temple... and perhaps receive some healing. ~
@496   = ~Never mind.  I have intruded.  Farewell.~
