@1474  = ~[no text]~
@1475  = ~I believe you said monsters were of concern. Are they a problem here?~
@1476  = ~[no text]~
@1477  = ~I will take my leave of you now. Farewell.~
@1478  = ~A sore subject that one is... It seems they're on the rise lately. More monsters are spotted in the surrounding countryside every day. Orcs, goblins, you know the like. It has people worried.~
