@1485  = ~Why, this is the best tavern in all of Kuldahar. The food is good, the ale isn't watered down, and the service is friendly. ~
@1486  = ~[no text]~
@1487  = ~I will take my leave of you now. Farewell.~
@1488  = ~I don't rightly know what to say about Kuldahar. It's a bit of a wonder. I'll give it that. The only thing that allows the town to survive is the great tree and the warmth it provides... It doesn't seem right somehow...~
