@1807  = ~Very well, then. I will go speak to the barkeep.~
@1808  = ~Oh, that so? Well, we should all be blessed, then, our bone-carving neighbors trudging through the drifts to make sure we're all right. What's Easthaven worried about us for?~
@1809  = ~We heard of strange events in the region - goblins, orcs, and other humanoids seem to be gathering in Easthaven... and Kuldahar. Do you have any idea why?~
@1810  = ~No, no, I don't - I mean, we've had our share of raiders before, but this year's been worse than any other I can recall. ~
