@2028  = ~We spoke with Sister Calliana, the acting head priest of the Temple of Ilmater in Kuldahar. She's assumed the role of head priest of the temple ever since Mother Egenia vanished a few weeks ago.  Calliana also mentioned that another member of the Ilmater clergy, a man by the name of Brother Poquelin, passed through Kuldahar recently from all the way from Cormyr and was going to try and get help from the Monastery of the Weeping Lilac in Bryn Shader.  Calliana fears he may have been abducted as well. ~
