@2079  = ~We told that idiot Jhonen the "cause" of his dreams, and we convinced the fool to give up all his worldly possessions and leave the town. It only came to some knucklehead trout, a knife and some evil satisfaction, but we'll take what amusement we can in this backwater frontier town. ~
