@2181  = ~To have come this far, you must be seeking death.  I will grant it to you, interloper.~
@2182  = ~Do not concern yourself with my true form.  This is my... servant.  He acts as my eyes and mouth.  And now he shall act as my sword.~
@2183  = ~You!  You have no right to profane Talona's power.  She is a goddess of awesome vile majesty.  You will bow before her when I offer you in sacrifice, holy warrior!~
@2184  = ~Yes.  You are well learned.  It took me many years to learn the necromancy to augment my priestly powers.  It is nice to find someone who appreciates the dark arts.  It is a pity my minions have to destroy you now.~
@2185  = ~You will not live to regret those words, fool.~
