@2598  = ~Can it be that you know nothing of the Lord of the Dead? Ah, well. It matters not. All things living know of Him eventually.~
@2599  = ~So, Myrkul is a death god?~
@2600  = ~We seek a strong warrior to accompany us. Would you be such a person? ~
