@2733  = ~~
@2734  = ~I'm Aldwin, and maybe the winter winds have frozen your ears -- do you want a *room* or not? My inn's the only inn in town, so don't even be thinking you'll find a better deal anywhere else.~
@2735  = ~~
@2736  = ~I'd watch your tongue, innkeeper. I'm not in the mood to quarrel with you. ~
@2737  = ~~
@2738  = ~~
