@2744  = ~I'll be on my way, then. Farewell.~
@2745  = ~Yeah... why? Somebody in town saying different?~
@2746  = ~Well, I found this ring upstairs. It seems to put the ownership of the Evening Shade in question.~
@2747  = ~Amelia, the barmaid at the Root Cellar mentioned you. She said you bought this inn from a man named Eidan. Before he vanished, that is.~
@2748  = ~No, just curious. Do you have any rooms free?~
@2749  = ~~
@2750  = ~Never mind. I think I'll be on my way. Farewell.~
