@3336  = ~Sune's Laurel of Favor~
@3337  = ~This wreath of laurel leaves and roses was a gift from the church of Sune to the priestesses of Hanali Celanil at the Hand of the Seldarine.  The representatives of the human goddess of love and beauty were well received and the high priestess of Hanali Celanil wore the laurel whenever humans were visiting the Hand.  The orcs discarded the laurel as useless trash when they sacked the priests' tower.

