@4059  = ~[KHALID 15] Sunny or not, 'tis nice to enjoy the out-of-doors~ [KHALD15]
@4060  = ~[KHALID 16] Even with infravision I prefer the daylight.~ [KHALD16]
@4061  = ~[KHALID 17] C-Can I help you?~ [KHALD17]
