@4174  = ~[QUAYLE 20] I'm too smart for this.~ [QUAYL20]
@4175  = ~[QUAYLE 21] Is that all?~ [QUAYL21]
@4176  = ~[QUAYLE 22] There's none better.~ [QUAYL22]
@4177  = ~[QUAYLE 23] I am so smart!  S  M  R  T!  I mean  S  M  A  R  T!~ [QUAYL23]
