@4179  = ~[QUAYLE 25] Feel my amazing brain!  Go on, touch it!~ [QUAYL25]
@4180  = ~[QUAYLE 26] I wile away the hours, conferring with the flowers, consulting with the rain.~ [QUAYL26]
