@4239  = ~[TIAX 41] Ha Ha HA!  Smart guy dies, and Tiax goes on to RULE!~ [TIAXX41]
@4240  = ~[XZAR 1] Montaron, you are so AGGRAVATING!  'Tis disturbing to my demeanor!~ [XZARR01]
