@6281  = ~The Vale of Shadows.  My brother Silas and I made a pilgrimage there to pay our respects to our family crypt, like we do every year, but this time... I don't know; the Vale seems... different... *cursed,* somehow.  The shadows have come alive, and there's yetis roaming the paths, attacking travelers.  ~
