The caster utters the finger of death incantation, points his index finger at the creature to be slain, and unless the victim makes a saving throw vs. spells, the victim dies instantly.  Even if the save is successful, however, the brush with death still inflicts 3-17 points of damage.  Characters slain by a Finger of Death cannot be resurrected - they are gone forever.~
