At the culmination of this dreadful spell, the wizard screams like a banshee (groaning spirit).  For each level of the caster, one listener within 30 feet hears the wail.  Those who fail a saving throw vs. death magic die instantly.
     The caster is not affected by the spell, but cannot choose who will be affected.  Creatures who cannot hear due to ear plugs or deafness may be targets but cannot be affected and automatically make their saving throws.~
