@7758  = ~I believe I've been to the elven outpost you're looking for.  It is a ruined tower that lies deep in the mountains south of Kuldahar.~
@7759  = ~~
@7760  = ~It looked as though it had seen better days.~
@7761  = ~Not bad, considering that it was destroyed hundreds of years ago by a cataclysmic spell that wiped out its inhabitants and cursed them all into an eternal existence of unlife. ~
