Mages need not always be mages -- Tenser's Transformation changes the caster into a heroic fighter, doubling the wizard's hit points, and gives him a +4 bonus to his armor class. All damage the caster sustains takes away from the bonus hit points first. All the wizard's attacks have the same chance to hit as a fighter of the same level, and the wizard is allowed to attack twice a round with +2 damage per attack.
