@7993  = ~No need for that, I'll be on my way.~
@7994  = ~Oh bother, I don't have the time nor the patience to detail the history of this place for you.  You are an adventurer, are you not?  Revel in the joys of being one and venture beyond my chambers... now.~
@7995  = ~You will answer my question... now.~
