@7997  = ~AGAIN you return!  What could you POSSIBLY want now?~
@7998  = ~I just wanted to let you know that I single handedly solved the mystery of Larrel's daughter's disappearance, disposed of the evil lich that had overrun the cemetery, AND in doing so allowed the ancient dwarven spirits to finally find their peace.~
