@8000  = ~Nothing, just wandering around.  I'll leave now.~
@8001  = ~Well intrude is what you've very well done now, isn't it? How might I quickly send you on your way?~
@8002  = ~~
@8003  = ~Don't bother, I'll just leave right now.~
@8004  = ~If you must know, my name is Bandoth.  I study magics, and I am very particular about my work and privacy.  So, if there's nothing more, I'd ask that you'd leave me be.~
@8005  = ~I have some questions I'd like to ask you.~
@8006  = ~I think I'll just snoop around for a bit, if you don't mind.~
@8007  = ~I'll leave you to your work.~
@8008  = ~Ask and be quick about it!~
@8009  = ~I ran into a umber hulk who claimed he used to be a Red Wizard of Thay named Saablic Tan.  Do you know anything about him?~
@8010  = ~I spoke with an ancient elven lich named Larrel whose daughter went missing in these parts ages ago.  Do you know anything about her?~
@8011  = ~What can you tell me about this area?~
@8012  = ~What do you know of the dwarves who used to occupy these caves?~
@8013  = ~I don't like your tone, old man.~
@8014  = ~Never mind.  I'll depart.~
@8015  = ~You have tested my patience since the moment you stepped foot in my home.  I suggest that you leave now before I demonstrate some of my recent endeavors for you.~
@8016  = ~Please demonstrate, if you don't mind.~
@8017  = ~What if I want to stay and make myself at home?~
@8018  = ~Okay, okay!  I'll get out of your hair.~
