@8235  = ~A ring is a small band of precious metal that is used as jewelry.  Some rare rings have had enchantments placed upon them that confer various magical abilities.  These rings are highly sought after, especially by those of the adventuring profession. For no apparent reason, this ring feels warm to the touch.

STATISTICS:

Resistance Bonuses:
 +10% Missile Resistance
 +10% Fire Resistance
~
