@8463  = ~The level you are standing on is a commons area where you will find our festhall, tavern, and the store of yours truly, me.  From this level, you can obviously see the five towers that protrude from here:  Corellon Tower, Sheverash Tower, Sehanine Tower, Labelas Tower, and Solonor Tower. ~
