@8479  = ~I am looking for the orog chieftain.~
@8480  = ~Did you know that there's an Umber Hulk in these caves that used to be a Red Wizard of Thay?~
@8481  = ~Just passing through.~
@8482  = ~You have found him.  What do you want?~
@8483  = ~I have come to obtain your badge.~
@8484  = ~I suggest you defend yourself.~
