@8726  = ~Kaylessa's Gloves~
@8727  = ~Why, OF COURSE it's true.  All of it!  I could tell you tales of women SWOONING at my feet after reciting a few lyrics from my songs.  You see, it all has to do with this voice I was born with.  Some would say that a voice like mine could only be a gift from Corellon himself.  But I'm not one to boast.~
@8728  = ~Worn by Kaylessa, weapons master of the Seldarine's Hand.  Her prowess in archery only bested by her beauty, Kaylessa was devoted to hone the battle skills of any elf under her.  If there were any heroes at the Battle of Seldarine's Hand, Kaylessa was one of them.  She was a shining example of courage in the face of impending doom as she fearlessly led her people against orc and goblin hordes.  Even after the fall of the Hand, her commitment to battle and her people remained strong.  Her last wish was to die in glorious battle.

