@8885  = ~Marketh is a horrible human.  He enslaves my people for his lord, Revered Brother Poquelin.  Salamanders, led by Shikata, abuse my people and force them to work in the old refineries and mines of Dorn's Deep.  The salamanders are incredibly cruel, often forcing my people against walls just to burn them to death.~
