@9761  = ~Yeti Pelt~
@9762  = ~These thick pelts are valued for their incredible durability and warmth.  Locals from the Ten-Towns pay good money for the pelts, as few would be so bold as to hunt the yeti in their homeland.  Some of the Reghedmen barbarians hunt yeti as a rite of passage into manhood.~
@9763  = ~Giant's Sleep~
@9764  = ~This weapon was used by the human ranger Althax Grom.  Althax hated the giants that plagued his homeland and was trained to exterminate them from a young age.  Although Althax originally fought his foes using the sword and bow, he quickly decided that those weapons were too slow against his huge foes.  His druid friend, Eladan, enchanted this hammer for him.  The reputation of the weapon grew as legends of Althax grew.  Even though the warhammer has passed through many hands since Althax's untimely demise, Giant's Sleep will always be remembered as the weapon of that powerful warrior.

