Cold Resistance:  +20% bonus
Weight:  3
~
@10032 = ~Due to the extremely volatile nature of most magics, Mage Robes of Fire Resistance are not uncommon among young acolytes and their wizardly tutors. As with other such robes, they can not be worn except by mages

