@10817 = ~Marketh has a ring that he uses to teleport all over Dorn's Deep.  If you could make a copy of that ring, we might be able to switch it and trap him.~
@10818 = ~Never mind, Norl.  Farewell.~
@10819 = ~I know that ring well, but not that well.  If I could get hold of the ring itself, I could do it.  Otherwise, I don't believe I'd be able to make an accurate copy.~
@10820 = ~Well, I do have a drawing of him that I got from two sculptors.  It shows his ring in great detail.  Would that do the trick?~
@10821 = ~Hmm.  That is a problem.  I'll try to figure something out.  Farewell.~
