@10825 = ~No, but I do have a drawing of him from two sculptors.  It shows the ring in great detail.  Would that do the trick?~
@10826 = ~No, not yet.  Sorry.  Farewell.~
@10827 = ~I'm sorry, but the ring's not ready yet.  Come back later and I'll have what you need.~
