@10831 = ~You failed to copy the spell to your mage book.~
@10832 = ~I'm not gonna serve you another drop; you can barely stand as it is. Best you sleep it off before you go out lookin' for trouble.~
@10833 = ~Ah!  The ring is finished, gracious allies.  Here it is, a silver band with a big fat emerald for Marketh's big fat head.  It won't be easy to switch them, I'd imagine, but Callarduran will be with you.~
@10834 = ~Spectator~
@10835 = ~Thanks, Norl.  Farewell.~
@10836 = ~Let me know when you give Marketh the punishment he has coming to him.  I can't wait to see his reign of terror come to an end.~
