@10842 = ~I am Lord Chamberlain Marketh.  I'm responsible for making sure that New Dorn's Deep runs efficiently, among other things.~
@10843 = ~Even if you have to crush a few gnomes into the ground to do it, eh?~
@10844 = ~Lord Chamberlain?  New Dorn's Deep?  That's a little pretentious, don't you think?~
@10845 = ~Ah.  Marketh.  You're the guy who likes beating up women.  You must feel like a really big man.~
@10846 = ~You have?  Terrific!  News travels quickly even on the outskirts of the Underdark, it seems.  I'm glad to see that New Dorn's Deep is getting a reputation.~
@10847 = ~Not permitted to buy/sell items.~
@10848 = ~New Dorn's Deep?  It seems like New Dorn's Deep is nothing more than a slave camp.  Aren't you being a little pretentious?~
@10849 = ~Protected by Minor Spell Turning~
