@10891 = ~Ah, but this dream *will* come true, my friends.  There is nothing anyone can do to stop it.  Now, if you'll excuse me, I have some business to attend to.~
@10892 = ~Ha!  We'll see who's crazy when our forces march across Icewind Dale.  It will truly be a sight to behold.  Now, you must excuse me.  I have someplace I'd rather be right now.~
