@13930 = ~No, that's the tower of Orrick the Grey.  Fortunate we are to have a wizard this far north.  Friendlier than most spell-casters I've known; he values his privacy, but I still see him tip back a tankard or two with the best of them at the Root Cellar.  He's got some goblin that does chores for him.  ~
