@14899 = ~I am Urnst, the p-p-potter... at least I used t-to be.  Now I just want to g-get out of this place alive.  But with all the t-terrible things happening in town, I'm too scared to step outside m-my shop.~
@14900 = ~Th-this shop is my home.  I used to make pottery here, b-but there doesn't seem to be much point anymore.  I've closed shop and packed up m-my things.  As soon as the p-pass is clear, I'm heading south to Baldur's G-gate.  I hear it's nice there.~
@14901 = ~Dis-disturbances?  Yes.  People disappearing, m-monsters everywhere... even the weather has t-turned against us.  Nobody knows why... not even Arundel.~
@14902 = ~He watches out for us.  Some s-say he's the last of the old druids of K-k-kuldahar.  His house is just south and west of here, over by the s-standing stones.~
