@15344 = ~For a week, we held the horde back.  Entrenched in our home, my people fought and the horde paid dearly for every room of the Hand they took.  For every elf that fell, the horde paid tenfold.  For all the sacrifices my people made, the last line was breached in a week's time. ~ [LARR_40]
@15345 = ~~
