@15731 = ~We returned and told that foolish sea spirit Elisia that we had "delivered" the blade to Jhonen.  She swallowed the lie like a fish swallows bait, and she even *rewarded* us for our efforts.  We can only pray that other creatures we meet in the North are as gullible.~
