@15749 = ~I am not interested in your feeble-minded perceptions.  The Shard is nothing but a tool to me.~ [BELH_03]
@15750 = ~I have used its power to further my plans and gain advantage where none existed before.  I am *its* master.~ [BELH_04]
@15751 = ~[no text]~
@15752 = ~[no text]~
@15753 = ~Nevertheless, your conquest is at an end.  This land will not fall to you or to the influences of the Shard.~
@15754 = ~Now who's being feeble-minded?  It is you who has been used by Crenshinibon.  And now that you have failed to serve its purposes, the Shard has betrayed you.~
@15755 = ~Believe what you wish.  Now you must die.~
@15756 = ~Please.  Do not insult me with such transparent lies.  Deception is a delicate art form and should not be practiced by one as clumsy and inexperienced as yourself.~ [BELH_05]
@15757 = ~Burial Isle~
@15758 = ~Dryad of the Cloudpeaks~
@15759 = ~Dryad of the Cloudpeaks~
@15760 = ~[no text]~
@15761 = ~[no text]~
@15762 = ~We asked Kerish, the frost salamander leader, for the key to the surface exit.  He agreed to give it to us. ~
@15763 = ~Unfortunately for you, I am not so clumsy and inexperienced in the ways of battle.~
@15764 = ~It is no lie.  How do you think we got here?  The Shard led us to you.  It *wants* us to destroy you.~
@15765 = ~Impossible!  Crenshinibon serves me.  It has obeyed my commands all along, aiding my cause and-~ [BELH_06]
@15766 = ~It served you only to serve its self.  Its evil is fueled by the desire for conquest.  But reopening this portal is not conquest... it's madness.  What will be left to rule once the minions of hell are set free in this world?~
@15767 = ~I care nothing for ruling *this* miserable land.  The scope of my desire is far beyond your mortal comprehension.~ [BELH_07]
@15768 = ~I exist solely for the purpose of corrupting the corruptible.  To me, this world is nothing but a fertile field, a vast crop of temptable souls.  ~ [BELH_08]
@15769 = ~And now... it is harvest time!  Consider yourselves fortunate!  You alone shall witness this historical moment!~ [BELH_09]
@15770 = ~Behold!  The circle is complete!  What was undone so long ago has been done once more.  The doors to the Lower Planes have been thrown wide!~ [BELH_10]
@15771 = ~And now my brethren are free to plunder this world for its immortal spoils.  Soon, the ranks of the Blood War army will swell with thousands of fresh souls! ~ [BELH_11]
@15772 = ~[no text]~
@15773 = ~Too bad you won't be around to see it.  Your time in this world is over.~
@15774 = ~Fools!  Do you think you can defeat me so easily?!  The priest has done nothing but delay the inevitable!~ [BELH_12]
@15775 = ~[no text]~
@15776 = ~[no text]~
@15777 = ~[no text]~
@15778 = ~I still possess the secrets of unlocking the portal!  It is only a matter of time before I open the gate once more.~ [BELH_13]
@15779 = ~[no text]~
@15780 = ~Marketh's concubine, Ginafae, has agreed to switch Marketh's ring of teleportation with a fake that I had Norl make.  She told us to come back in a day. ~
@15781 = ~You won't get the chance.  Your time is over.~
@15782 = ~Perhaps you are nauseated by the realization that my actions, however appalling they might seem, serve a greater good. ~ [BELH_14]
