@16167 = ~Thank Silvanus you have returned!  Evil is afoot in Kuldahar.  Strange orcs prowl through town, killing our townspeople!~ [FAB_01]
@16168 = ~I must ask you... have you found the source of evil in Dragon's Eye?~ [FAB_02]
@16169 = ~Perhaps.  A strange "woman" named Yxunomei was raising an army of trolls, lizard men, yuan-ti, and undead.  I defeated her and many of her minions.~
