@16368 = ~Would that I could.  The face of the evil remains hidden, but its presence is unmistakable.  All about us, there are signs of its damaging influence on the balance... the unnatural weather, the recent rash of abductions, the numerous monster sightings in the pass...  ~ [ARUN_08]
