@17618 = ~Girdle of Stromnos~
@17619 = ~The enchanter Presdon of the Vast created this girdle several hundred years ago for his bodyguard, Dendes the Wry.  He named the broad belt after a hill giant who had almost killed him when he was looking for spell components.  Dendes died defending Presdon from rival mages near Ordulin.

