@17636 = ~Boots of the Forgotten Ones~
@17637 = ~These wrinkled, rough boots were made from the scalps of dead orc shamans from the Stinking Paw tribe.  The power hungry religious leader of the tribe, Algrash Who-Watches-In-Darkness, ordered his underlings to make the boots by digging up the corpses of his predecessors.  Algrash was killed when he provoked a fight with a gang of ogres.  His boots were left at the scene of the battle.

STATISTICS:

