@17669 = ~Boots of the Many Paths~
@17670 = ~Created by a gnomish illusionist in 931 DR, the Boots of Many Paths have been worn by a number of adventurers who have sold the items through legitimate means for many, many years.  According to their maker, Weldy Baker, the boots rely not only on the power of illusion, but the power of "potential time weave cutting and microscopic changes to minutiae in the environment that have macroscopic effects."

