User can cast Blur on themselves once per day.
~
@17671 = ~[Wounded, dying]At last... I feared I could not hold any longer... th-the last of my life has almost left my body, and... soon I shall be restored to the balance.~ [ARUN_82]
@17672 = ~Arundel... what happened? ~
@17673 = ~A man, but not a man... he wore my skin like a cloak, my face like a mask... he came suddenly in the night, and struck me down... ~ [ARUN_83]
@17674 = ~Nature itself seemed to recoil from him - even with the strength of the Great Oak bolstering me, I was unable to stop him.  He touched me once... his hands as blood, and I felt... my life begin to drain away.~ [ARUN_84]
@17675 = ~Arundel, hold on - we still may be able to help y--~
@17676 = ~[Voice strengthens, becomes steadier.]No, only the hope you would return has kept my body alive.  You... you must take the Heartstone Gem to... the elven fortress of the Severed Hand.  ~ [ARUN_85]
@17677 = ~Severed Hand?  But why?~
