@17730 = ~While serving Lord Geldon Adari at the Battle of Hollow Hills, an untrained peasant soldier named Kallin fought bravely to overtake and capture an important enemy wizard at extremely high risk to his personal safety.  As a reward for such incredible, selfless daring on Kallin's part, Lord Adari had an ally enchant a magical halberd for Kallin.  The soldier also received a small plot of land, which he oversaw as yeoman for the rest of his days.  When Kallin turned sixty, he passed the magical weapon to his young nephew, Vergarash.

Statistics:

