@17739 = ~These stairs look like they were purposely collapsed to prevent entry from the level below.~
@17740 = ~A powerful weapon and tool, this staff was created by the powerful archmage Ubath of the Celestial Sign.  Originally of Algarond, Ubath commanded great respect for his skills as a summoner of beasts and elementals.  Unfortunately, Ubath's desire for power drove him to extreme lengths.  His conjuring of extremely powerful entities from the lower planes is what eventually did him in.  This staff is his most prominent legacy.  It was left behind, slightly blackened, when he was dragged away to Acheron.

