@18865 = ~Ugh... how embarrassing.  Fine, here's my Black Dragon Scale... you know how hard it is to get this?  Here's my sword.  Uh, I don't suppose there's any chance you'd let me keep this ring around my neck, is there?  At least leave me *something.*~
