@18872 = ~Huge vats of molten metal bubble and hiss overhead.  Rust on the sides of the vats indicate that they must have been dormant for a long period of time.~
@18873 = ~This cart is filled with ore and stone debris.  The wheels are locked with rust.~
@18874 = ~Large glowing gemstones dimly illuminate this cavern.  Stone debris and tiny gemstones litter the ground.~
@18875 = ~Created through the Fire Seeds spell, these innocuous seeds are imbued with explosive fiery magic.

STATISTICS:

