@18888 = ~She cursed the vale and bid us to rise.  We could not deny her...  The calling...  It was too strong.~
@18889 = ~What calling are you talking about?~
@18890 = ~I see.  I must leave now.  Farewell.~
@18891 = ~I do not know...  I cannot explain.  We could not resist the calling...  I must leave now.  The land of the dead calls me home...  Farewell.~
