@21872 = ~I was speaking to the cooper, Tybald Dunn.  It seems to me his business could use some encouragement.~
@21873 = ~Ah, Tybald Dunn!  Yes, I was meaning to speak to him.  I've heard that Targos to the south is making plans to expand their shipping trade.  They would undoubtedly be in need of skilled coopers. ~
