@22398 = ~I... I... think he's hurt so bad he can't speak... after he fell, he cried out, buh... buh... but I haven't heard him in a while...~
@22399 = ~Your ability to spin a tale amuses me, Hailee.  Pray continue. ~
@22400 = ~~
@22401 = ~I... but my broth... oh, you're no fun!  You're as dumb and boring as the rest of this *stupid* town! ~
@22402 = ~I think a young girl could find more amusement in playing pitch pebble or old man's crutch than telling tales to strangers. ~
