@22408 = ~No, I spoke to your mother... and she told me you had no brother, Hailee, and that you'd best go home to your father. ~
@22409 = ~I won't go!  Let him make his stupid barrels all day, because I won't do it!  I *hate* it, and I *hate* him! ~
