@22445 = ~Hailee, I don't have time for guessing games.  Why did he buy the Inn? ~
@22446 = ~Cause it has a *magic mirror!*  Uh-huh, it's true!  I saw him step right through it... well, I mean, he *opens* it first, but it's *like* he's walking right through it!  ~
@22447 = ~I believe you.  I know of this door already.  Thanks for telling me, though, Hailee.~
@22448 = ~Are you telling another tale, Hailee? ~
@22449 = ~The mirror's a door?  Hmmm.  Perhaps I'll ask Kieran about it. ~
@22450 = ~It's true!  I saw him do it one night when I was chasing night flies outside!  I saw him through his bedroom window - he walked into his room and opened the mirror!~
@22451 = ~~
@22452 = ~Just don't tell him I told you, or else he'll put *me* in the mirror. ~
