@22463 = ~Wylfdene's Tribal Insignia~
@22464 = ~This is a large metal disk on a set of chain links.  It features the symbol of Wylfdene's tribe, the Tribe of the Bear.  It appears to have been deliberately defaced with a sharp object.~
@22465 = ~Okay, I'll share... I promise.  Now please tell me!  Pleeassse!~
@22466 = ~Ah, then here it is: I was fishing upon Dinneshere to the South, when I caught a knucklehead trout upon my line.  I was about to pluck it off and put it in my catch-basket, when it spoke to me!~
@22467 = ~All right, then... there's a huge bear out in the woods, and it, uh, asked me about you.  ~
