@22491 = ~Wh... Nuh-uh!~
@22492 = ~It's true... the secret *you* hold may hold the key to defeating the barbarian horde and saving your town.~
@22493 = ~Mother wants to leave because of them, but she *always* wants to leave... she says the barbarians are going to burn down Lonelywood. ~
