@22642 = ~Yes.  The storm of war darkens the skies of my homeland.  My people are gathering in numbers greater than any have seen for generations.  ~ [HJOLL009]
@22643 = ~Wylfdene[Wilf-dane] is his name.  He was a great warrior from an elder tribe who was slain in battle on the eve of last season.~ [HJOLL010]
@22644 = ~Shadow Thief Mage~
