@22661 = ~[surprised]The same.  You know our history well.  ~ [HJOLL014]
@22662 = ~Jerrod was our greatest hero.  Centuries ago, he united the tribes and led us to victory against invaders from the south.~ [HJOLL015]
@22663 = ~He died on the battlefield in the embrace of infernal magicks, bravely sacrificing his life to save his people.~ [HJOLL016]
