@22928 = ~Hrothgar asked us to find a missing caravan out of Caer-Dinival.  We told him that we had already come across the ambushed caravan and had tracked the marauding orc raiders back to their lair.  The stout warrior seemed somewhat worried about the orc attack, but was relieved to know that the supplies were still recoverable.~
