@23258 = ~Yeah, I should respect creatures dumb enough to walk into big metal jaws.  Right.  Like I said, you want company, go talk to Emmerich.  I'm through with you.~
@23259 = ~Well, this is exactly what I knew would happen.  That jackass Emmerich keeps us from trapping, and now some animal rips Digby apart.  I swear, that weak little ranger's gonna get his neck snapped.~
