@23275 = ~Braggart's words do not interest me.  If these are the deeds of a true warrior, then I will hear them.~
@23276 = ~I must take my leave of you.  Farewell.~
@23277 = ~Then perhaps at another time you shall.  For now, however, I would know why you have come before me.~ [WYLF002]
