@23534 = ~Seeing Tiernon's skill in forging ice, we recalled Murdaugh's tale in Lonelywood and asked Tiernon to craft a rose of ice.  As he worked the ice, the rose seemed to grow beneath his hands, almost blossoming as he sculpted it.  The rose's beauty is breathtaking. ~
