Special:
 +10 Maximum Hit Points within a dragon's flight of Lac Dinneshere
 Cast Cure Critical Wounds 3/day
 Grants wielder +3 STR 1/day
Weight: 3
Speed Factor: 2
Proficiency Type: Long Sword
Type: 1-handed
 
~
