@25227 = ~BEASTFRIEND: This druid has a deep and instinctive knowledge of the habitats, behaviors and actions of animals and feel quite protective of them.  They maintain a close relationship with animals and can gain their friendship easily.

Advantages:
* may instantly charm any animal (bear, wolf, lion and snake) for one day once per round.  The creature does not get a saving throw.

Disadvantages:
* may only shapeshift into a brown bear~
