@25597 = ~What's this?  Why look here, master Kieran.  It seems that Lady Tymora has blessed your coffers this season after all.  This hardy band of brave-looking souls will surely keep your kegs flowing well into the night!~
@25598 = ~That's the spirit!  Kieran here is the good barkeep of the Whistling Gallows.  He will gladly see to your refreshment, just as he so graciously nurtures my own fondness for libation.~
@25599 = ~Come now, Kieran.  You know that my heart is a cold and vacant tenement that will never again be occupied by such a fickle emotion as love.  I drink because it is the only thing left that I do well.~
@25600 = ~My name is Murdaugh of Auckney, wandering bard and failure extraordinaire.  Welcome to Lonelywood.  It is a pleasure to make your acquaintance.~
