@26331 = ~By exposing Wylfdene before the council, we've succeeded in stopping the war between the barbarians and the Ten-Towns.  However, it seems our quest is far from over.  Hjollder believes that the corrupt spirit that fled Wylfdene's body may still pose a threat to his people.  We've agreed to journey by ship to an island on the Sea of Moving Ice.  Once there, we are to hunt down the flown spirit and put an end to its evil once and for all.~
