@27214 = ~We managed to force a startling confession out of that halfling codger, Hobart.  It seems that he's been in league with the Luremaster all along.  He claims that he was forced into serving the ghost, and that he must continually bring adventurers to the castle or the riddling spirit will make a ghost out of him.~
@27215 = ~How many others have come through here?~
@27216 = ~Right.  May I look at the goods you've collected?~
@27217 = ~Thank you for telling us.  Farewell, Hobart.~
