@27225 = ~Salutations to the travelers.   Welcome to Castle Maluradek[Mah-loo-rah-dek].  I am your adversary.~
@27226 = ~There is the matter of our disagreement.~
@27227 = ~Vallah's Hand~
@27228 = ~You remove the ring from the finger and it tingles in your palm. There is obviously something special about the ring. ~
