@29208 = ~Spider Spawn (Conjuration/Summoning) 
Level: 4
Range: 40 yards 
Duration: 5 rounds + 1 round/level
Casting Time: 6
Area of Effect: Special 
Saving Throw: None 
Upon casting this spell the wizard must throw several spider eggs (which is the material component) into the air while saying the final command word.  The result is that the eggs morph into fully grown spiders that will remain under the wizards telepathic control.  The type of spiders that appear depend upon the level of the wizard casting the spell.  
7th : giant spider
9th : phase spider
12th+ : sword spider
When the spell is cast there is a 20% chance that two spiders of the proper type will appear instead of just one.  These spider(s) will remain under the wizards control until effected by a dispel magic, slain, or the spell duration expires.~
