@34296 = ~A fallen priest of Ilmater named Brother Perdiem told us about how he came under Revered Brother Poquelin's spell.  Apparently, Poquelin appeared at Perdiem's temple some time ago and hypnotized the entire congregation.  They left their monastery and moved north, many dying along the way.  Poquelin was able to covert an entire temple of devout Ilmaterian priests.  Who is he to be able to do such things?~
